1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,630
Some paths feel closer the moment confidence returns.
当安心回来，自然也不再遥远。

2
00:00:02,630 --> 00:00:05,890
A steady ride can make the outdoors feel welcoming again.
稳定前行，让户外重新变得亲近。

3
00:00:05,890 --> 00:00:09,570
Not to hold him back. Just to share the way forward.
不是拦住他，而是陪他继续向前。

4
00:00:09,570 --> 00:00:11,620
Beyond mobility. We defend dignity.
超越移动，我们守护尊严。
